  "text": "It was impossible to assess the impact of the new N130K mutation based on clinical data, because only the 58R/ 117N double mutant was observed in isolates from the patients enrolled in the clinical trial of SP efficacy, including the isolate with the A383G mutation in pvdhps. The use of yeast constructs might facilitate interpretation of the role of this mutation in resistance [CITATION_1] .",
